ew-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Misleading. There is no actual subdirectory or subfolder created for each lanaguge in the root, so there are zero SEO benefits. Those who understand SEO know what I mean. If there is no subdirectory where all your translations are stored and accessed from a url like domain.com/es there are no SEO benefits. A plugin database is not a subdirectory</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A great plugin for WordPress!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergioburgos/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c86eb38e5529aa0add6129ac66d8cc1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c86eb38e5529aa0add6129ac66d8cc1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergioburgos/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sergioburgos</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Gennaio 30, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It\'s a great tool. It has allowed me to create a multilingual site in a very simple way. Many thanks to its developers!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<